data_table.description: Subject ID, sample ID, sample source, source sample ID, sample use, and study ID variable of participant with uterine cervical adenocarcinoma and involved in the "HeLa Cell Genome Sequencing Studies" project.

variable.name: SAMPLE_USE
variable.description: Sample use. Seq_DNA_Chromatin: Chromatin sequencing; Seq_DNA_SNP: SNP genotypes derived from sequence data; Seq_RNA: Whole transcriptome sequencing

variable.name: STUDY
variable.description: DbGaP top-level (parent) study and/or sub-study accession: phs000640=parent study; phs000642=sub-study; phs000643=sub-study
